data.meta_description: Julia III Augusta Caesonia was born on 30 Oct 39 BC in Roma, Lazio, Italy, daughter of Gaius Julius Caesar Octavianus AUGUSTUS 1st Emperor of the Roman Empire, and Scribonia Di Roma. She was married in Rome, Italy to Marcus Vipsanius Agrippa Postumus, She was married in Roma, Lazio, Italy to Marcus Vipsanius Agrippa Postumus, She was married in the year 21 BC in Rome, Italy to Marcus Vipsanius Agrippa Postumus, She was married in Roma, Lazio, Italy to Marcus Vipsanius Agrippa Postumus,, they had 3 children.., they gave birth to 1 child. She died on 10 Jun 13 BC in Reggio di Calabria, Calabria, Italy. This information is part of Richard and Charlotte Allen Cosby Ancestry by Richard Cosby on Genealogy Online.
